                    <ul>
                        <li>
                            Finalize grant-making model
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            Perform first distributions of grants
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="subsection">
            <div class="card card--center">
                <img src="/images/icons/avatar.svg">
                <h2>Members' Club</h2>
                <p>
                    Members are individuals who donate at least $1,000 per year. They have formal governing rights at
                    OSE. They participate in selecting the grant-distribution model, and they nominate community members
                    to fill seats on the board of directors.
                </p>
                <p>
                    OSE is guided by Members with “skin in the game”, giving them a direct voice in how their donations
                    support open source. All OSE board members must also be Members.
                </p>
                <a href="#donate" class="button">
                    Donate now<span class="after">›</span>
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    <section>
