                        permanent principal, which is not spent.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="card">
                    <img src="/images/icons/suns.svg">
                    <h3>
                        <span class="process-number">2</span>Investing
                    </h3>
                    <p>
                        The endowment principal is invested in a diversified, low-risk portfolio that generates
                        sustainable annual returns. We target a ~5% spend rate, typical for US universities.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="card">
                    <img src="/images/icons/balls.svg">
                    <h3>
                        <span class="process-number">3</span>Grant-Making
                    </h3>
                    <p>
